Name: You Will Never Get This Achievement
About the game: You have too much free time and nothing else to do? You feel like something is missing in your life? You like to push buttons? If all of the above apply to you, you should certainly acquire this game! Click as fast as you never clicked before in your life. But I warn you: YOU WILL NEVER GET THE LAST ACHIEVEMENT! Features: Fully functional funky options menu! Super serious and silly achievements! - One achievement for every cent you pay! Six extra ordinary music compositions! Costs less than a Dollar! Your score gets saved between your sessions! (You don't need to cry if you accidentally quit the game) Buy it for your friends, they will hate it! Good Luck!
